==English==
===Etymology===
Shortened form of '''electronic commerce'''.
=== Noun ===
{{wikipedia}}
'''e-commerce'''
# [[Commercial]] activity conducted via the [[Internet]].
===Style===
'''e-commerce''' when used in the body of a sentence or paragraph.
'''e-Commerce''' when used at the beginning, or in the body, of a headline or title where all significant words are capitalized.
'''E-commerce''' only when used at the beginning of a sentence.

